Code preview of the table BC_展位异动方案拟撤场

alter table "BC_OutBrand"
drop constraint FK_BC_OUTBR_REFERENCE_BC_BOOTH;

drop table "BC_OutBrand" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "BC_OutBrand" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "BC_OutBrand"
(
"OutID" NUMBER(32) not null,
BCD NUMBER(32) not null,
"StoreyID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"BoothID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"BoothCode" VARCHAR(20) not null,
"IsAssboothAdjust" INTEGER,
"ContractCode" VARCHAR(20) not null,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"IsInnerAdjust" INTEGER,
"Reason" INTEGER,
"ReasonRemarks" NVARCHAR2(2000),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Status" INTEGER,
"UpdateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"IsAbolish" INTEGER,
"ParentBoothID" NUMBER(32),
constraint PK_BC_OUTBRAND primary key ("OutID")
);

comment on column "BC_OutBrand"."StoreyID" is
'目的：用于获取整个楼层的撤场次数';

comment on column "BC_OutBrand"."IsAssboothAdjust" is
'1:调整
0：不调整';

comment on column "BC_OutBrand"."Status" is
'拟撤场
已生效（方案创建合同，合同生效且撤场生效；方案创建合同，合同取消且撤场生效）
已废除（方案废除）';

alter table "BC_OutBrand"
add constraint FK_BC_OUTBR_REFERENCE_BC_BOOTH foreign key (BCD)
references "BC_BoothChange" (BCID);
